title: Data Activism
description: I curated a curriculum that integrated social justice and data science to encourage minoritized high school students to pursue a career in STEM.

title: Corporate Investor Data Analysis
description: Performed an exploratory data analysis on Metropolitan Area Planning Council(MAPC) dataset which contained census information and corporate ownership rate for each neighborhood in the Boston area.

title: RL Computational Tool
description: I made a website that hosts a self-driving game. I made this computational tool as a part of a research opportunity program to enable middle school and high school students learn about reinforcement learning concepts.

title: Interactive MapBox Visualization of BlueBike Stations
description: I utilized mapbox to visualize the total traffic of blue bike stations. And allow the uers to be able to filter based on time of day.
